{"tid":1684752,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"本港第3季經濟按年收縮2.9%　10年來首次下跌","createTime":"2019-10-31T09:05:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T09:14:02.000Z","uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bebb2e0030492d54a2d507d8ca1df9c17e83bb01","tid":1684752,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:05:23.000Z","msg":"本港第3季經濟由升轉跌，政府公布第3季本地生產總值(GDP)預先估計數字，經濟按年實質跌2.9%，是10年來首次下跌，差過第2季的升0.4%，由於內部及對外需求表現疲弱。<br />\n<br />\n經季節調整，上季經濟按季亦跌3.2%，連續兩個季度錄得按季跌幅，反映經濟已步入技術性衰退。首3季經濟按年亦收縮0.7%。<br />\n<br />\n第3季政府消費開支升幅則加快至5.3%，但私人消費開支按年倒跌3.5%，是逾10年來首次下跌。政府發言人指，內部需求明顯轉差，經濟下滑削弱消費情緒，連串大型示威活動對零售、飲食及其他消費相關行業造成重大干擾。<br />\n<br />\n經濟信心低迷，整體投資開支跌勢加劇，本地固定資本形成總額按年跌幅擴大至16.3%，連跌4個季度。貨品進出口、服務輸出及輸入，這4項數據都下跌。本地社會事件重創訪港旅遊業，服務輸出創逾16年來最大跌幅。<br />\n<br />\n政府將於11月15日公布第3季GDP修訂數字、更詳細的統計數字，以及今年全年GDP修訂預測。"},{"pid":"00ac901fba0dca5a2b966dbf8d30470689178399","tid":1684752,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:05:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1489259-20191031.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1489259-20191031.htm&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnA%2FMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=f0cce8f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1489259-20191031.htm&h=339970fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1489259-20191031.htm</a>"},{"pid":"3b9909865bdca1a7687508e2016fbf6396301bc8","tid":1684752,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:06:05.000Z","msg":"終於都收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"298fe3b1e7549a1de2de8ccbe3133f1ec4b9ac60","tid":1684752,"uid":106252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:09:46.000Z","msg":"跌咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a456458893ad05d6162339eccc17e93280269f49","tid":1684752,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:14:02.000Z","msg":"molamola<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}